products.name: Plain Nonfat Greek Yogurt
products.categories: Dairies, Fermented foods, Desserts, Fermented milk products, Dairy desserts, Fermented dairy desserts, Yogurts, Greek-style yogurts

products.name: Evaporated Milk
products.facts: ["Evaporated milk is made from fresh milk that has had about 60% of its water content removed.","It is often packaged in cans, which are recyclable and help reduce food spoilage.","Evaporated milk is shelf-stable, meaning it can be stored at room temperature until opened, reducing energy use for refrigeration during transport.","Quality evaporated milk contains no added sugars or preservatives, ensuring a more natural product."]
